<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>
    CANCELLATION: {{ client_name }} – {{ showroom_location }}
  </title>
</head>

<body style="margin:0; padding:0; background-color:#f3f4f6; font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#374151;">

<table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background:#f3f4f6; padding:24px 12px;">
<tr>
<td align="center">

<table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="max-width:970px; background:#ffffff; border:1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius:8px;">
  <!-- Body -->
  <tr>
    <td style="padding:24px 24px 20px 24px; font-size:16px; line-height:16x; color:#374151;">

      <p style="margin:0 0 20px 0; line-height:16x;">
        The following booking has been cancelled by the client and the time slot has been released back to the website.
      </p>

      <p style="font-weight:bold; margin:0 0 05px 0; line-height:16x;">Booking Details:</p>

      <ul style="font-size:16px; margin:0; padding-left:30px; line-height:1.7;">
        <li style="line-height:1.7;"><strong>Client:</strong> {{ client_email|default('N/A') }}</li>
        <li style="line-height:1.7;"><strong>Time:</strong> {{ original_time|default('N/A') }} [{{ time_zone|default('AEST (GMT+10:00) Time in Sydney NSW') }}]</li>
      </ul>

      <p style="margin:20px 0 0 0; line-height:16x;">
        <strong>Next Steps:</strong> The event has been automatically removed from the Google Calendar. No further action is required.
      </p>

    </td>
  </tr>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <tr>
    <td style="padding:0px 24px 0px 24px; font-size:16px; line-height:16x; color:#374151;">
      <p style="margin:0 0 20px 0; line-height:16x;">Best regards,</p>
      <p style="margin:0 0 20px 0; line-height:16x;"><strong>Krost Website Booking System</strong></p>
    </td>
  </tr>

</table>

</td>
</tr>
</table>

